description: This file imports the root registration function from 'expo', imports the main App component, and registers the App component as the root component of the application using 'registerRootComponent'. It serves as the entry point for the Expo-based React Native application, ensuring proper environment setup and component registration.

methods.name: registerRootComponent
methods.description: Registers the specified component as the root component of the app and sets up the environment for either Expo Go or native builds.
